pageProduct.description:
General Information

Evening Primrose Capsules

Warnings

Vitamin supplements should not replace a balanced diet

Common Uses

Evening Primrose Oil is a good source of Linoleic acid (LA) and gamma-Linolenic acid (GLA) Omega-6 fatty acids, which both help to maintain general health and wellbeing
This formula:
? Maintains general health and wellbeing
? Is a natural source of Omega-6 fatty acids
? Contains Evening Primrose Oil, supporting which supports skin health and maintains skin integrity
? Created for Vegan and Vegetarians

 

Ingredients

Each capsule provides
Evening Primrose Oil  1g (1000mg)
Equiv Linoleic acid          650mg
Equiv gamma-Linolenic acid 100mg
